---
import TelegramIcon from "@assets/icons/Telegram.astro";
---

<section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-900 to-gray-800 py-8">
  <div
    class="container mx-auto h-full min-h-[80dvh] flex items-center justify-center max-md:flex-col gap-4 px-4 md:px-8"
  >
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <h1
        class="text-4xl leading-tight max-md:text-center lg:text-5xl tracking-tight font-bold text-white [&>span]:text-[#F7DF1E]"
      >
        Aprende y mejora tus habilidades en <span>JavaScript</span>
      </h1>
      <p
        class="md:max-w-[80%] text-xl text-gray-400 lg:text-2xl max-md:text-center"
      >
        Únete a nuestra comunidad de desarrolladores y lleva tus conocimientos
        al siguiente nivel.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div
      class="w-full lg:max-w-[40%] rounded-sm bg-gray-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm p-6 md:p-8 shadow-lg border border-gray-700/50 h-fit"
    >
      <form>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6 max-md:text-center">
          Únete a nuestro grupo de Telegram
        </h2>

        <label for="name" class="text-gray-300">Nombre completo</label>
        <input
          type="text"
          class="bg-gray-700/50 border-gray-600 text-white placeholder:text-gray-500 focus:border-[#0088cc] transition-colors outline-none rounded-sm w-full p-2 mb-4 mt-1"
          autocomplete="off"
          placeholder="Nombre completo"
        />

        <label for="email" class="text-gray-300">Correo electrónico</label>
        <input
          type="text"
          class="bg-gray-700/50 border-gray-600 text-white placeholder:text-gray-500 focus:border-[#0088cc] transition-colors outline-none rounded-sm w-full p-2 mb-4 mt-1"
          autocomplete="off"
          placeholder="Correo electrónico"
        />

        <button
          class="w-full bg-[#0088cc] hover:bg-[#0077b5] text-white font-bold py-2 text-md lg:text-lg transition-all duration-300 rounded-sm cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-center"
          type="button"
        >
          <TelegramIcon class="inline-block mr-2" />
          Unirme a Telegram
        </button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
